body.prompt:
URGENT: New {{ .event.diff.after.properties.severity }} incident created: {{ .event.diff.after.title }}

Incident ID: {{ .event.diff.after.identifier }}
Affected Service: {{ .event.diff.after.relations.affected_service }}
Triggered by Deployment: {{ .event.diff.after.relations.triggered_by_deployment }}

Please investigate immediately:
1. Get details about the affected service and its tier
2. Check deployments to this service in the last 48 hours
3. Look for any suspicious PRs or changes
4. Find who is on-call
5. Form a hypothesis on root cause
6. Recommend a specific action

Write your findings back to incident {{ .event.diff.after.identifier }} in the triage_summary field.
